data.description: This charming ranch-style home, only a year old, awaits you in a prime location. Step onto the inviting farmers porch with composite decking. Inside, discover hardwood floors, recessed lights, and an open layout spanning the living, kitchen, and dining areas. The kitchen boasts white cabinets, stainless steel appliances, and quartz countertops. Bedrooms feature plush carpeting, with the primary bedroom offering dual large closets. A partially finished basement provides a 418 sq/ft bonus room for entertainment or play, along with ample storage or workshop space. Outside, a fenced backyard with a stone paver patio is perfect for recreation and hosting BBQs. Enjoy energy efficiency with on-demand hot water, propane HVAC, and city utilities.
